 ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xd the great","CreatedById":188222,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-31T10:35:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223513021\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022180944\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221546124671\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022194287\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Patrick C\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\nOn 12/30/2018 at 7:04 AM, Patrick C said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut how do i use the \u0022tweakscale\u0022 or find sounding rockets ?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFind sounding rockets by searching.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed9682333784\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/92434-13-sounding-rockets-start-small-dream-big-050/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:227px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTweakscale is just tweaking size of stuff. Other variables such as volume will increase/decrease accordingly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222019-01-31T10:45:27Z\u0022 title=\u002201/31/2019 10:45  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00225 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 31, 2019\u003C/time\u003E by Xd the great\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Terwin","CreatedById":139655,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-31T13:50:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTweakscale is also a 